[title]De_dust_p2[/title]
-------------

Well. After a few weeks learning hard, I had one-week holiday. So come back with happy mapping, my fav work
This map is in my project "making with dust style". I still continue learning all source mapping features and creativity. This time, it's smaller than de_dust_p1, however, not square map.

[b]Feature:[/b]
1. 3D skybox
2. Fog
3. Ambience
4. Bird flying effect (make flying path smoother)
5. Wind
6. Support up to 64 player
7. Fairly high FPS (I think)

Hope people enjoy it. Please comment and vote for me
